// NO type assertions without validation
const user = data as User;                        // ❌
```

### 5.3 Type Safety Checklist

- [ ] No `any` types
- [ ] No `@ts-ignore` comments
- [ ] No type assertions without validation
- [ ] Proper interfaces for all data structures
- [ ] Null checks with optional chaining

